      "content": "Fable 5 开放 Anthropic (@AnthropicAI) We’ve received notice that the Department of Commerce has lifted export controls on Claude Fable 5 and Mythos 5. We'll begin restoring access tomorrow, and will share an update soon. We’re grateful to our users for their patience, and to everyone who worked with us on redeploying the models. — https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2072106151890809341#m",
